snippet.title: Diana and Roma - Wash Your Hands story
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma - Wash Your Hands story. Story time for kids.
Diana and Roma do not want to wash their hands before eating. Their stomach hurts and needs to be treated. Now the children will understand how important it is to wash their hands.
